resources.string: Vula i-Talkback ukuze uthole imininingwane eyengeziwe
Ibonisa uma izenzo zamakhasimende zikhona ngento yamanje.
I-TalkBack iiwuhlelo lokufunda isikrini ikakhulukazi sabantu abanokungaboni kanye nokubona okuncane. Ivumela ukuhlanganyela nedivayisi kusetshenziswa impendulo ekhulunywayo.
Thola impendulo ekhulunywayo ukuze usebenzise iwashi lakho ngaphandle kokubheka isikrini.
